{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","title":"OUDSRadio","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"role":"symbol"},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio button is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Radio button that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a Radio button to be displayed."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:isReadOnly:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponen